text:
Keepin' It Reel, Episode 304: Our Biggest Star Wars: The Force Awakens Questions 
Welcome back to Keepin' It Reel! In this week's episode of IGN's movies podcast, Jim Vejvoda, Terri Schwartz and Chris Carle bring you the latest in genre movie news. 
This week's topics include: our reactions to and lingering questions raised by the new trailer to Star Wars: The Force Awakens; Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice; Fantastic Four; Ant-Man and the Wasp; Captain America: Civil War; Die Hard 6; Doctor Strange; Gambit; Chris Rock returning to host the Academy Awards; Back to the Future Day; and more. 
We also discuss this week's new releases: The Last Witch Hunter, Jem and the Holograms, Paranormal Activity: The Ghost Dimension, Rock the Kasbah, Suffragette, and Attack on Titan: End of the World.
